Ingredients:
 - 1 litre of water
 - 100 gram rice
 - 1 teaspoon salt
 - 1 1/2 teaspoons chilli powder
 - 1 teaspoon Turmeric powder
 - 3 teaspoons oil
 - 1/2 cup vegetable oil
 - 1 teaspoon mustard
 - 2 potato 
 - 2 tomato
 - 1 teaspoon Garam Masaala

Directions:
 1. Put oil in cooker. After it becomes hot then put mustard, peices of potato and tomato, Garam Masaala
 
 2. Wash the rice with water and put it into the cooker. Then put salt into it. Then put water.
 
 3. Keep it in cooker for around 20-25 minutes.